column298: We had the most amazing afternoon with Duong on the Tales of Saigon walking tour. Her openness and her incredible passion for history, architecture, design, and her culture gave us such a deeper understanding of the city and region we were visiting. She shares so intimately and carefully the intricacies of what makes Saigon unique from the foods, to the neighborhoods and all the small details that can be easily overlooked. We had high hopes that the walking tour would give us a deeper understanding of the history and especially architecture of the city and it more than delivered thanks to Duong being such an incredible guide for us. We felt so lucky to have her detailed view of her culture, and her city which set us up perfectly to continue to explore on our own.
